msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/transform_distort_perspective/rotate_keyframable.rst:46
msgid ""
"The axes for rotation are different than for moving a clip. The latter"
" uses "
"the monitor plane: X = width or horizontal axis, Y = height or vertical "
"axis. For rotation the plane is tilted by 90 degrees \"into the monitor\" "
"and rotated 90 degrees clockwise around the vertical axis. This results"
" in "
"the X axis coming out of/going into the monitor, the Y axis being along"
" the "
"width of the monitor and the Z axis being along the height of the"
" monitor. "
"See image below."
msgstr ""

